\[
y = \frac{2x-1}{x+5}
\]
Let's solve for $x$:
\begin{align*}
y(x+5) &= 2x-1 \\
yx+5y &= 2x-1 \\
yx-2x &= -1-5y \\
x(y-2) &= -1-5y \\
x &= \frac{-1-5y}{y-2}
\end{align*}
